<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes primarily maintain the alliance rather than fire. However, light fires in montane and subalpine meadows usually do them little harm; they help to maintain meadows (Ratliff 1985).</div>
